and ultimately this city forever.

648
00:52:55,465 --> 00:52:57,967
If we don't have the courage
and the conviction

649
00:52:58,051 --> 00:53:00,970
to fight this war
the way it should and needs to be fought,

650
00:53:01,054 --> 00:53:04,432
